WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:04.368
[Madame Kali] <i>She's the one
the Master seeks above all.</i>

00:04.370 --> 00:06.203
What do you want of me?

00:06.205 --> 00:08.705
Sometimes you tie a lamb
to lure a lion.

00:08.707 --> 00:10.807
The Wolf of God.

00:10.809 --> 00:13.076
<i>Stand alongside
the great winged Lucifer</i>

00:13.078 --> 00:15.712
<i>as he reconquers
heaven's bloody throne.</i>

00:15.714 --> 00:18.582
[Lily] <i>My beloved immortal.</i>

00:18.584 --> 00:21.285
This sad little world is ours.

00:21.287 --> 00:23.219
[Lavinia] Let's go explore
what Father's been building.

00:25.289 --> 00:27.023
[Octavia]
<i>Animals are right in cages.</i>

00:27.025 --> 00:28.391
You can't keep me here.

00:28.393 --> 00:29.726
But of course we can.

00:29.728 --> 00:30.960
[Rusk] <i>Ethan Talbot.</i>

00:30.962 --> 00:32.762
<i>You will not take
one step from this house</i>

00:32.764 --> 00:33.930
<i>when you will not be observed.</i>

00:33.932 --> 00:36.632
Cornered animals
are the most dangerous.

00:36.634 --> 00:38.068
But they are cornered,
nonetheless.

00:38.070 --> 00:39.802
- You're not real.
- [laughing]

00:39.804 --> 00:40.936
You're not here.

00:40.938 --> 00:42.104
[Frankenstein]
<i>Sir Malcolm's in trouble.</i>

00:42.106 --> 00:43.706
I will not
let him suffer alone.

00:43.708 --> 00:47.142
What if Miss Ives should prove
stronger than you think?

00:47.144 --> 00:48.977
If I were of
another constitution,

00:48.979 --> 00:50.713
I would fear you.

00:50.715 --> 00:51.847
She's gone.

00:51.849 --> 00:53.749
Oh, for fuck's sake!
Get the others!

00:53.751 --> 00:55.150
[Lyle] <i>You have no idea</i>

00:55.152 --> 00:56.885
<i>what hell
you are stepping into.</i>

00:56.887 --> 00:59.121
Welcome to my home, Miss Ives.

00:59.123 --> 01:01.190
- [gasps]
- [hisses]

01:01.192 --> 01:03.325
- Sir Malcolm...
- [gasps]

01:03.327 --> 01:04.626
It's Doctor Frankenstein.

01:04.628 --> 01:06.195
[Creature] Father.

01:06.197 --> 01:07.562
Your children have returned.

01:10.133 --> 01:11.200
[Ethan] <i>I can't stop it!</i>

01:11.202 --> 01:12.534
[snarling]

01:14.169 --> 01:16.271
I need to see
Sir Malcolm immediately.

01:16.273 --> 01:18.440
There's someone else
you need to see first.

01:18.442 --> 01:20.475
[Vanessa]
<i>So, I'm to meet your Master?</i>

01:20.477 --> 01:22.344
[Madame Kali]
<i>He's your Master as well.</i>

01:25.180 --> 01:26.548
Murderer.

01:27.650 --> 01:29.650
<i>♪</i>

